{"serial": "63002", "department_serial": 59, "code": "SS1002", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Space Science and Engineering", "ch": "太空科學與工程導論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chang, Chee-Wei"], "ch": ["張起維"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S4", "room": "807"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "太空科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Space Science and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 6, "selected": 31, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "太空的探索與應用跨多種科學與工程領域，隨者人類對太空通訊、遙測、導航、與科學探索的日益增加，我們必須要了解太空環境、系統與科學探索之間的關係，以及與現代社會的關聯。本課程將對這些太空環境與探索的多元領域進行概論介紹，以作為後續更專精學研基礎。", "en": "Space is an interdisciplinary domain requiring the integration of multiple fields of science and engineering. The growing utilization of space for communications, remote sensing, navigation, and scientific exploration nessecitates a general understanding of these different aspects of the space environment, space systems, and its relation to modern society. This class provides a broad introduction to these multiple fields related to the space environment and space exploration, serving as a foundation for more in-depth future studies."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 太空概論：太空環境與應用\n2. 太陽物理與日地關係\n3. 行星科學與太陽圈物理\n4. 磁層物理\n5. 高層大氣科學\n6. 電離層物理\n7. 雷達與遙測\n8. 軌道運動學概論\n9. 衛星導航原理\n10. 太空仔劇概論：太空系統與生命週期\n11. 太空通訊概論\n12. 太空電力次系統概論\n13. 太空政策與法律概論", "en": "1. Introduction to Space: Environment and Application\n2. Heliophysics and Solar-Terrestrial Physics\n3. Planetary Science and Heliophysics\n4. Magnetospheric Physics\n5. Upper Atmospheric Physics\n6. Ionospheric Physics\n7. Introduction to Radar and Remote Sensing\n8. Introduction to Orbital Mechanics\n9. Introduction to Satellite Navigation\n10. Introduction to Spacecraft: Systems and Lifecycle\n11. Introduction to Spacecraft Communications\n12. Introduction to Spacecraft Electrical Power Subsystems\n13. Introduction to Space Policy and Law"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Johnson, C. D. (2017). Handbook for new actors in Space. Secure World Foundation.\nhttps://swfound.org/handbook/\n\nFleeter, R. and H. Given (2000). The Logic of Microspace (The Space Technology Library, Vol. 9). Microcosm, Inc.\nhttps://www.amazon.com/Logic-Microspace-Space-Technology-Library/dp/1881883116", "en": "Johnson, C. D. (2017). Handbook for new actors in Space. Secure World Foundation.\nhttps://swfound.org/handbook/\n\nFleeter, R. and H. Given (2000). The Logic of Microspace (The Space Technology Library, Vol. 9). Microcosm, Inc.\nhttps://www.amazon.com/Logic-Microspace-Space-Technology-Library/dp/1881883116"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "作業 / 小考: 50％\n期中考: 25％\n期末考: 25％", "en": "Homeworks / Quizzes: 50％\nMidterm: 25％\nFinal: 25％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "S4-806. 星期五 10:00 – 11:00 或另約時間。", "en": "S4-806. Friday 10:00 – 11:00 or by appointment."}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "2 weeks end of semester reserve.", "en": "2 weeks end of semester reserve."}, "domain": {"ch": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n磁層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n行星科學與太陽圈物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n太陽物理與日地關係\n\n\n、\n\n\n雷達與電磁波觀測\n\n\n、\n\n\n太空酬載\n\n\n、\n\n\n衛星遙測\n\n\n、\n\n\n基礎學科", "en": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n磁層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n行星科學與太陽圈物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n太陽物理與日地關係\n\n\n、\n\n\n雷達與電磁波觀測\n\n\n、\n\n\n太空酬載\n\n\n、\n\n\n衛星遙測\n\n\n、\n\n\n基礎學科"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "太空科學知識的建立", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "日地系統觀測技術的培養", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "整合創新與獨立思考", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "資料分析能力的養成", "rating":